path.aria-label: The only requirements are that no external source of current
(pull-up resistor or current source) be on the B-pins of the TCA980x.
Option 2: TI_TCA9801DGKR, if there are no pull-up resistors or current source on the OLDI LCD, can install U7.
Option 1: TI_PCA9306DQER, if there are pull-up resistors on the OLDI LCD, must install U31.
As there are 10K pull-up on the OLDI LCD, so install U31 default.
